## **Running the Jupyter Notebooks**  
The notebooks **`tasks.ipynb`** and **`project.ipynb`** can be run in any code editor, such as **Visual Studio Code**, or using the web application **JupyterLab**.

The notebooks include:
- Solutions and analysis for both tasks and project assessments.  
- References to research performed as part of the assessments.

